OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FMonday should get off to a
OL,6,Ffine start with some sunshine.
OL,7,FHowever, showers will break out during
OL,8,Fthe day, turning locally heavy and
OL,9,Fthundery. Feeling less chilly with
OL,10,Fgentle winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FAfter
OL,13,Fanother chilly start Tuesday looks set
OL,14,Fto be a dry and bright day. Turning
OL,15,Fwet and windy overnight into
OL,16,FWednesday. Sunshine and showers
OL,17,Freturning on Thursday. Temperatures
OL,18,Frising slightly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
